CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FThose who placed a replica of a mosque
OL,7,Fon top of a bonfire have an "agenda
OL,8,Ffull of hate and bigotry towards
OL,9,Fothers", a judge has said.
OL,11,FDistrict judge Barney McElholm made
OL,12,Fthe comments as he refused bail to a
OL,13,Fman charged with incitement to hatred
OL,14,Flinked to the loyalist bonfire in
OL,15,FMoygashel, Co Tyrone.
OL,17,FBrian Conrad Neill, 56, of Hollow
OL,18,FMills, Newmills, Dungannon, appeared
OL,19,Fin the dock of Dungannon Magistrates'
OL,20,FCourt in handcuffs on Friday.
OL,26,@oD@]OUqD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FThe alleged offence Neill is charged
OL,7,Fwith occurred on Wednesday, the night
OL,8,Fthe mosque was placed on the bonfire,
OL,9,Fwhich has received widespread
OL,10,Fcondemnation.
OL,12,FThe court heard he is accused of
OL,13,Fthreatening, abusive or insulting
OL,14,Fbehaviour or displaying written
OL,15,Fmaterial which was threatening,
OL,16,Fabusive or insulting intending to stir
OL,17,Fup hatred or arouse fear.
OL,19,FNeill confirmed to the court he
OL,20,Funderstood the charges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FA detective constable said she was
OL,7,Faware of the circumstances of the case
OL,8,Fand could connect the accused to the
OL,9,Fcharge.
OL,11,FDuring an application for bail, the
OL,12,Fofficer said police were made aware on
OL,13,FWednesday night of a structure being
OL,14,Fadded to the top of the Moygashel
OL,15,Fbonfire, which was covered by a blue
OL,16,Ftarpaulin.
OL,18,FShe said there were around 70 to 100
OL,19,Fpeople in the area and some males were
OL,20,Fobserved on top of the bonfire, some
OL,21,Fwearing dark clothing and balaclavas.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FShe said one male on top of the
OL,7,Fbonfire was not wearing a face
OL,8,Fcovering and appeared to be assisting
OL,9,Ftwo masked men in pulling up two signs
OL,10,Fto be screwed on to the bonfire.
OL,12,FOne sign said "Secure our borders" and
OL,13,Fother said "End the threat of radical
OL,14,FIslam".
OL,16,FShe said when the blue tarpaulin was
OL,17,Fremoved, a "mosque-like" structure was
OL,18,Fleft on top of the bonfire.
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@bO]uD@LOUvD@FO]yD@LOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FThe officer said it included Arabic
OL,7,Fwriting which had been translated as
OL,8,F"Islamic Fascism". She said the males
OL,9,Fthen made their way down the bonfire.
OL,11,FNeill was seen getting into a car and
OL,12,Fwas then stopped by police and
OL,13,Farrested, she told the court.
OL,15,FThe officer said he told police during
OL,16,Finterview he had been asked by two
OL,17,Funknown males wearing balaclavas to
OL,18,Fassist in pulling the two signs up the
OL,19,Fbonfire.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FShe said he had said he had then
OL,7,Fclimbed down the bonfire before the
OL,8,Ftarpaulin could be removed and was not
OL,9,Faware what was below it.
OL,11,FShe said he had denied hatred of those
OL,12,Fof the Muslim faith.
OL,14,FThe officer objected to bail on the
OL,15,Fbasis of fear that Neill would offend
OL,16,Fagain and would be likely to ignore
OL,17,Fbail conditions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FShe said there was a "strong public
OL,7,Ffeeling" about the offence and said
OL,8,Fpolice had dealt with a "potential
OL,9,Fserious public order situation" at the
OL,10,Fbonfire site on Thursday night.
OL,12,FShe said police believe Neill is
OL,13,F"influential" in the Moygashel area.
OL,15,FA defence solicitor said his client
OL,16,Fhad confirmed at police interview that
OL,17,Fhe was the unmasked individual on top
OL,18,Fof the bonfire.
OL,26,@nD@VOUoD@HO]pD@YOUqD@_O]uD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FHe said the tarpaulin had been removed
OL,7,Fafter his client had climbed down from
OL,8,Fthe bonfire.
OL,10,FThe lawyer said his client had arrived
OL,11,Fin Moygashel on Wednesday night to
OL,12,Fmeet some friends when he had been
OL,13,Fapproached by two masked men who had
OL,14,Fasked him to fix a "crooked" part of
OL,15,Fthe bonfire structure, due to his
OL,16,Fexpertise as a tree surgeon.
OL,18,FHe said Neill did not know a replica
OL,19,Fof a mosque was under the tarpaulin.
OL,26,@vD@TOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FHe said his client "played no part" in
OL,7,Fthe Moygashel Bonfire Association,
OL,8,Fwhich had erected the bonfire.
OL,10,FHe said: "He was used by the more
OL,11,Fsinister elements in this group."
OL,13,FDistrict Judge McElholm said the
OL,14,Fdefendant was asking the court to
OL,15,Fbelieve he "just happened upon this
OL,16,Fincident".
OL,18,FHe said the Moygashel bonfire was
OL,19,F"notorious" and that if he or any
OL,20,Freasonable person was asked to help
OL,21,Fwith it they would "recoil in horror".
OL,26,@nD@TOUnD@cO]rD@JOUsD@aO]wD@LOUxD@IO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@KO]}D@TOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FThe judge said: "We have seen what
OL,7,Fthey have been putting on top of the
OL,8,Fbonfire in recent years, a police car,
OL,9,Fa small boat full of immigrants.
OL,11,F"Needless to say the Moygashel bonfire
OL,12,Fhas become notorious.
OL,14,F"It seems as if on each year they try
OL,15,Fto outdo the disgraceful nature of
OL,16,Fwhat they did the previous year.
OL,18,F"They don't need tree surgeons, they
OL,19,Fhave been doing this for years."
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783874992
OL,3,CThose behind Moygashel bonfire 'full
OL,4,Cof hate and bigotry'
OL,6,FThe district judge said there were
OL,7,Fmany bonfires in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fwhich go off "completely peacefully".
OL,10,FHe said: "The people who run this
OL,11,Fparticular bonfire have a clear
OL,12,Fagenda, it is an agenda full of hate
OL,13,Fand bigotry towards others."
OL,15,FThe district judge refused bail. Neill
OL,16,Fwas remanded in custody until August 5.
